                    "title": "Speed",
                    "transformCode": "/**\n * Speed Transform: m/s → km/h\n * \n * Converts instantaneous velocity from meters per second (HSL native format)\n * to kilometers per hour (human-readable).\n * \n * Formula: speed_kmh = speed_ms × 3.6\n * \n * Handles:\n *   - Null/missing values → returns 0\n *   - Negative values → passes through (shouldn't occur in practice)\n */\n\nfunction transform(value) {\n  const speedKmh = (value || 0) * 3.6;\n  return Math.round(speedKmh * 10) / 10;  \n}\n",
